description.standard: New Music Daily is the playlist that never sleeps, updated regularly with new music you can’t miss. Today’s cover star is Venezuelan electronic artist and producer Arca (Alejandra Ghersi) with her latest track “Sola.” Have a listen and add this playlist to your library to stay up on the latest must-hear new songs.
description.short: Listen to “Sola,” the latest track from Venezuelan electronic producer Arca.
